<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
  <h2>Your Voucher Has Been Assigned</h2>

  <p>Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

  <p>We are pleased to inform you that a voucher has been assigned to your application.</p>

  <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Voucher Details</h3>
    <p><strong>Voucher Code:</strong> <%= @voucher.code %></p>
    <p><strong>Value:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@voucher.initial_value) %></p>
    <p><strong>Expiration Date:</strong> <%= (@voucher.issued_at + Policy.voucher_validity_period).strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
  </div>

  <h3>Important Information</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Your voucher is valid for <%= (Policy.voucher_validity_period / 1.day).to_i %> days from today</li>
    <li>The minimum redemption amount is <%= number_to_currency(Policy.voucher_minimum_redemption_amount) %></li>
    <li>You can use this voucher at any of our approved vendors</li>
    <li>Keep your voucher code secure and do not share it with others</li>
  </ul>

  <p>To use your voucher, simply present the code to any of our approved vendors. They will verify the code and process your purchase.</p>

  <p>If you have any questions about using your voucher, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>

  <p>Best regards,<br>
  The MAT Program Team</p>
</div>
